[src:1789-in-the-united-states/1789-in-the-united-states] Events from the year **1789 in the United States**.
[src:1789-in-the-united-states/1789-in-the-united-states] The Articles of Confederation, the agreement under which the nation's government had been operating since 1781, was superseded by the Constitution in March of this year.
